00:18:27.560 --> 00:18:31.240
and not let my favorite characters
die, I went on and when I was 12

00:18:31.240 --> 00:18:37.110
or 13, I painted this, and as it
goes down in Bloom County legend,

00:18:37.110 --> 00:18:39.570
it was my first cartoon,
and I didn't realize it.

00:18:39.570 --> 00:18:43.870
I handed it in as an art
project to Mrs. Lewis' class,

00:18:43.870 --> 00:18:51.850
and she gave me an F. So I showed
it to my father, who probably is

00:18:51.850 --> 00:18:54.870
to either get credit or blame for
my sense of humor and he looked

00:18:54.870 --> 00:18:57.850
