my destiny at that point.

00:19:41.290 --> 00:19:45.290
But, believe me, I'm coming
back around to Harper Lee.

00:19:45.290 --> 00:19:46.740
Don't forget.

00:19:46.740 --> 00:19:52.350
When it came time to invent a comic
strip in the Washington Post here

00:19:52.350 --> 00:19:55.110
in town, didn't know
what to suggest to me.

00:19:55.110 --> 00:19:56.410
I didn't know what
I should be doing.

00:19:56.410 --> 00:19:58.220
I knew I should be
doing a college cartoon

00:19:58.220 --> 00:20:00.210
that you can't sell to
a regular newspaper.

00:20:00.210 --> 00:20:02.530
