into marketing so much,

00:20:07.520 --> 00:20:10.250
that you would've come up
with a brand or a gimmick

00:20:10.250 --> 00:20:14.900
or a more catchy idea
for your strip.

00:20:14.900 --> 00:20:16.200
I had nothing.

00:20:16.200 --> 00:20:18.720
