some funny characters in a place.

00:20:18.720 --> 00:20:20.090
What would that place look like?

00:20:20.090 --> 00:20:24.090
Well, it would look like Maycomb
County from To Kill a Mockingbird.

00:20:24.090 --> 00:20:27.130
And when it came time to draw the
damn thing, I was just drawing

00:20:27.130 --> 00:20:29.810
To Kill a Mockingbird, and when
I populated it with characters,

00:20:29.810 --> 00:20:33.840 position:56%
it was children, it was parents that
was there to comfort their kids.

00:20:33.840 --> 00:20:39.520
When it came time to draw a
house, this was in Iowa City,

00:20:39.520 --> 00:20:43.270
I drew the house of --
