00:21:11.470 --> 00:21:19.240
Forty years after that little
boy's letter to Ms. Lee in 1967,

00:21:19.240 --> 00:21:21.950
I get this piece of fan mail.

00:21:21.950 --> 00:21:25.170
"Dear Mr. Breathed, this is
a plea from a dotty old lady

00:21:25.170 --> 00:21:28.730
from others not dotty at all,
please don't shut down Opus.

00:21:28.730 --> 00:21:31.270
Can't you at least
give him a reprieve?

00:21:31.270 --> 00:21:33.890
