this on the level that I did.

00:21:59.690 --> 00:22:05.340
But when you get a gift from
the gods like this, as a writer,

00:22:05.340 --> 00:22:07.800
you don't easily dismiss it.

00:22:07.800 --> 00:22:11.080
And I received these at a
time when I really wasn't

00:22:11.080 --> 00:22:13.010
