00:22:13.010 --> 00:22:17.710
When her book, her new book came
out, and I'd realized that she was

00:22:17.710 --> 00:22:22.110
at the end of her life, and
her franchise was threatened

00:22:22.110 --> 00:22:25.450
with a bad move, and her
characters -- when I say franchise,

00:22:25.450 --> 00:22:27.890
