of her characters.

00:22:27.890 --> 00:22:30.090
I thought back about
mine, and I thought back

00:22:30.090 --> 00:22:33.420
about the letter she had written me
some years before imploring me not

00:22:33.420 --> 00:22:36.230
to quit, combined with
those other two things,

00:22:36.230 --> 00:22:39.740
which is my story telling I
wanted to get back control of,

00:22:39.740 --> 00:22:43.490
Hollywood couldn't give it to
me, and great times were coming

00:22:43.490 --> 00:22:49.160
to be a comic strip writer.

00:22:49.160 --> 00:22:51.680
I decided to go back.

00:22:51.680 --> 00:23:00.380
