it fun to begin with,

00:23:03.100 --> 00:23:06.160
because I had quit Bloom County
because it had stopped being fun

00:23:06.160 --> 00:23:12.030
in 1989, which is what most people
stop a successful enterprise,

00:23:12.030 --> 00:23:13.340
is because they become bored.

00:23:13.340 --> 00:23:15.690
And when you become
bored, your guys are going

00:23:15.690 --> 00:23:17.470
