00:23:21.060 --> 00:23:23.500
Bill Watterson, I'm
sure, did the same thing.

00:23:23.500 --> 00:23:25.030
Gary Larson did, too.

00:23:25.030 --> 00:23:29.340
Unfortunately other strips
haven't taken the cues.

00:23:29.340 --> 00:23:31.280
That's the approach that we --

00:23:31.280 --> 00:23:35.290
